{"tid":293433,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[拯教港足]覺唔覺得馬會應該要開賭香港波","createTime":"2017-06-22T07:19:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-22T11:53:06.000Z","uid":113728,"like":25,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"086533bf672908dba9839fcbf844c3659f9a6df9","tid":293433,"uid":113728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T07:19:16.000Z","msg":"香港足球最大問題都係資金問題，年年開季都好像會唔夠隊開季咁。<br />\n覺得馬會應該開賭香港波。跟住把賭香港波的盈利一部份比聯賽獎金，例如冠軍有5千萬，亞軍有3千萬，就算包尾都會有幾百萬，起碼夠營運到隊波。<br />\n就好像英超球隊有大量的轉播費，咁球隊才有錢請球員，令球員有價值，生計得到保障，而教練，隊醫等後勤才請到專業人士。可能可以叫埋馬會做公關，令港超聯宣傳包裝得更好。球隊競爭才會更激烈。現在就算你拎曬香港所有比賽的獎金，都不夠養隊波，邊搵到夠多老闆去投資。 <br />\n至於防止假波，就類似賽馬咁，每場波都要有場監，如發現假波，就要重罰終生停賽\b，承之前所講，當球員生計得到保障，自然唔會咁容易放棄自己前途。至於有人話會令更加多人賭，咁就更加廢話，現在要賭，咩巴甲，挪超，連隊隊名都未聽過都有得開賭啦，最緊要都係睇你個人本身有冇定力。<br />\n另外政府可以把資助杯賽or 贊助球隊的金錢可以當退稅。那就更加可以吸引機構贊助。機構投資係好重要，就好像以前快譯通對好易通，精工對寶路華。大家都投放不少金錢，外援，令賽事有話題又有激烈。"},{"pid":"a9bb524ce25a16d9149e19a3bdfd3b582eb3621d","tid":293433,"uid":33053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T07:27:56.000Z","msg":"宜家每場波都有場監<br />\n不過如果一個場監咁易睇得出有人打假波<br />\n咁球迷都睇得出啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ce722e33a299e365b01ca7b5be9cab5c8c4ff90","tid":293433,"uid":16256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T07:29:24.000Z","msg":"聽講如果當初唔係足總清高 早就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9ceb0d25049dc0d27f5802c4772919dfd25359a","tid":293433,"uid":57374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T07:30:45.000Z","msg":"icac : 唔好啦掛"},{"pid":"c03ac5b6745699a62d1c74de4a41eb249a4ebf23","tid":293433,"uid":91875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T07:31:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>聽講如果當初唔係足總清高 早就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"404560d53432fdb3fa12f45dc1b391521be95dd2","tid":293433,"uid":91875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T07:31:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>icac : 唔好啦掛</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 前排先查完飛馬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10d00de6a9e7beb9078308f1e53cfcf6db5561ae","tid":293433,"uid":91875,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T07:33:32.000Z","msg":"其實而家香港足球真係靠市民支持先勉強維持到, 反正現時港足都係垂死階段,真係咩方法都值得一試"},{"pid":"468151dfda2d08a891ee0bc35f27683503d55c39","tid":293433,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T07:33:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>icac : 唔好啦掛</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 前排先查完飛馬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nicac請多廿條team都唔掂<br />\n唔開香港波好正確 但馬會支持下香港波 <br />\n馬會搞既野其實幾唔錯"},{"pid":"7e5aacbd0ddf769d7cb38d49d047f1256046861e","tid":293433,"uid":91875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T07:34:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>icac : 唔好啦掛</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 前排先查完飛馬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nicac請多廿條team都唔掂<br />\n唔開香港波好正確 但馬會支持下香港波 <br />\n馬會搞既野其實幾唔錯</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 社區盃係馬會SPONSOR, 不過獎金太少<br />\n我個人覺得賽馬都做到防假馬,我覺得波都容易<br />\n其實大陸有得睹香港波,要假波一樣會有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"690983d1aa8dd7bc36625013f5e30e223f7504f2","tid":293433,"uid":38991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T07:35:28.000Z","msg":"一早要 就算而家馬會唔開外圍都有開香港波<br />\n一樣有人打假波<br />\n賭仔輸比澳職日職D錢不如放返落香港足球好過"},{"pid":"afa492e50949d9984df1b4ce27c54f73f4d47f73","tid":293433,"uid":50882,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T07:37:13.000Z","msg":"贏錢正氣波 輸錢假波 是常識吧"},{"pid":"8391884047cd705a04e866bf11110d2e5ff27719","tid":293433,"uid":108120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T07:38:17.000Z","msg":"想賭好耐 一到睇現場一到賭下一隊入球 爽死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申 經常買飛入場睇"},{"pid":"5820a131949382e7aacc0f25594f3eb82eea000d","tid":293433,"uid":113728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T07:38:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>宜家每場波都有場監<br />\n不過如果一個場監咁易睇得出有人打假波<br />\n咁球迷都睇得出啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我意思係馬會增強監管的力度，就好像賽馬，一場投注都過千萬，但相對黎講叫公平，作假馬的難度較難。<br />\n同埋就算現在冇得合法投注香港波，久唔久都聽到有假波新聞，就係因為球隊人工低，令外圍佬用唔多的金錢就利誘到球員。咁不如開賭埋，再加大力度監管，起碼清白的球員都搵到食，專心踢波先"},{"pid":"3e79ed74ad0fdff767664b5ef69347583673b26f","tid":293433,"uid":91875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T07:40:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一早要 就算而家馬會唔開外圍都有開香港波<br />\n一樣有人打假波<br />\n賭仔輸比澳職日職D錢不如放返落香港足球好過</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢個真,只要限制球員唔準賭香港波就得"},{"pid":"557c28e8e669ecc0804b98934868b0cce3f80da0","tid":293433,"uid":91875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T07:41:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想賭好耐 一到睇現場一到賭下一隊入球 爽死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申 經常買飛入場睇</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 入場人數應該爆晒,個個廢中廢老入場當睇馬<br />\n嘩,呢件有屎痀,可ALLIN<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afcabb01da7e0a2b72487f0f3ce3f1db339506fa","tid":293433,"uid":91875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T07:42:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>宜家每場波都有場監<br />\n不過如果一個場監咁易睇得出有人打假波<br />\n咁球迷都睇得出啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我意思係馬會增強監管的力度，就好像賽馬，一場投注都過千萬，但相對黎講叫公平，作假馬的難度較難。<br />\n同埋就算現在冇得合法投注香港波，久唔久都聽到有假波新聞，就係因為球隊人工低，令外圍佬用唔多的金錢就利誘到球員。咁不如開賭埋，再加大力度監管，起碼清白的球員都搵到食，專心踢波先</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同意,合法化後將外圍問題帶返上水面處理,而家其實只係眼不見為淨"},{"pid":"23f1c6e6c94ab16fbde3ac5436b4dbb95fa47806","tid":293433,"uid":91875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T07:46:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 除左合法化賭波外,我覺得D波衫設計都要大大改善,隊隊都係組隊波衫款,又唔係間間有得公開賣<br />\n<br />\nBTW, 今年港會件衫好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb647e42d964bbc3778b6671edb9635a605d2dc9","tid":293433,"uid":113728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T07:55:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 除左合法化賭波外,我覺得D波衫設計都要大大改善,隊隊都係組隊波衫款,又唔係間間有得公開賣<br />\n<br />\nBTW, 今年港會件衫好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nYes, 提高獎金，令球隊有目標亦令球隊高層老闆有搵到錢的願景，咁自然會投資金，令球隊細微的地方都專業化，就好像球衣，球場布置等。越做得好，自然會更多球迷支持，更多支持就更會更上一層。更會帶動新職位和商機。"},{"pid":"acf862d6245ef313336b6810146f46a2dadc3c2b","tid":293433,"uid":48157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T08:32:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1f86fd8f7575e05dbd52f468282c2f9f60011708","tid":293433,"uid":48157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T08:33:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a3b46697dc115ee52435f0ca936be484105052ab","tid":293433,"uid":48157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T08:34:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a98b17c769428417127a320dfc4b5adeba6c21ac","tid":293433,"uid":56274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T08:42:13.000Z","msg":"其實當初係懶清高<br />\n同埋唔鼓勵賭博<br />\n而又想搵錢<br />\n<br />\n先傾掂數<br />\n<br />\n開賭波 唔開香港波"},{"pid":"2d47cc90135bcd43870a7767c6e56791af82aa07","tid":293433,"uid":91875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T08:43:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>想賭好耐 一到睇現場一到賭下一隊入球 爽死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申 經常買飛入場睇</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 入場人數應該爆晒,個個廢中廢老入場當睇馬<br />\n嘩,呢件有屎痀,可ALLIN<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個個坐 龍門後 角球旗位置 去屌波</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 球市真係復蘇"},{"pid":"802bbb1f78c818071a7fe6ce2a0db17d1a4256d3","tid":293433,"uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T08:59:24.000Z","msg":"我驚到時輸波，D人好似阿根廷聯賽D球迷咁，拎石頭扔死班球員 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e15bbf9e2693703f62346f327ae91a7731809d1","tid":293433,"uid":12458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T09:03:14.000Z","msg":"角球做馬應該睇唔出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}